.TH "alarmtimer_do_nsleep" 9 "alarmtimer_do_nsleep" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
alarmtimer_do_nsleep \- Internal alarmtimer nsleep implementation
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" alarmtimer_do_nsleep
.BI "(struct alarm *alarm "  ","
.BI "ktime_t absexp "  ","
.BI "enum alarmtimer_type type "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "alarm" 12
ptr to alarmtimer
.IP "absexp" 12
absolute expiration time
.IP "type" 12
alarm type (BOOTTIME/REALTIME).
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Sets the alarm timer and sleeps until it is fired or interrupted.
